ibe the same physical failure mode and therefore always co-occur at identical wind speeds.","is_correct":false,"explanation":"[Reverse Conditional] Reverse Conditional: It can be inferred that airflow separation and kinetic energy loss descr… cannot be proven solely from the premises given."}]'::jsonb, 'B', 'Step 1 — Identify stated logic
