ern craft breweries could authentically recreate every ancient recipe if archaeologists published complete chemical profiles from each shard.","is_correct":false,"explanation":"[Reverse Conditional] Equivocation: It can be inferred that modern craft breweries could authentically recre… cannot be proven solely from the premises given."}]'::jsonb, 'C', 'Step 1 — Identify stated logic
